  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the lentils and soak them in water for 30 minutes.",
    "In a large pot, saute the onion and garlic until softened.",
    "Add the jalapeno pepper and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin and paprika and stir to combine.",
    "Add the lentils, tomato sauce, and 2 cups of water to the pot.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "While the lentils are cooking, prepare the sopes by cooking the corn tortillas on a dry skillet for 30 seconds on each side.",
